  "background": "A noble of Esrolia, Aranda is proud and confident, her clothes and armor of fine make. As a devoted Axe Maiden of the bloodthirsty Earth goddess Babeester Gor, she is adorned with Runes of Earth and Death, broken by several fierce scars demonstrating that she is no dilettante. Now she travels throughout Dragon Pass, guided by her goddess, seeking worthwhile causes to wield her axe for.",
  "notes": "Front-line axe fighter with strong armor and nerve to hold a line. Carries herself like a noble of Nochet even when the axe comes out. Earth Shield is her anchor against huge hits. Slash is for ending fights fast. Berserker is for crisis only. Best passions are Honor, Loyalties, and Devotion to Babeester Gor. Death and Earth define her: grim, practical, and relentless.",
